{"tid":1418562,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"港島賽後檢討 - 無目標嘅戰爭","createTime":"2019-08-05T19:11:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T20:55:14.000Z","uid":63747,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"d5fa2634a76a36357468dd1db9f1e8a1b85dd42a","tid":1418562,"uid":63747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T19:11:14.000Z","msg":"長文<br />\n經過85同84呢兩日運動我發現大家都好似失去咗抗爭嘅目標咁<br />\n<br />\n港島Recap:<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><blockquote>朝早大家喺金鐘集會 <br />\n之後佔夏愨道再滅煙 <br />\n然後有人話唔好喺度捱打不如轉銅鑼灣 <br />\n去到銅鑼灣set完roadblock話去側魚涌警署 <br />\n經過北角打咗黑社會/比黑社會打咗 <br />\n去到側魚涌警署嗌咗兩下扔咗少少野入去狗屋之後比人射咗幾粒煙就退返北角<br />\n然後又話守銅鑼灣<br />\nSet完roadblock話快閃狗總 (有人快閃紅隧)<br />\n到狗總又係嗌兩句之後出土黑旗 連煙都未射就話有12架警車黎緊 所以要退<br />\n然後就無然後了</blockquote></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>1. 戰術上的失焦</strong><br />\n先勿論今日行動目的<br />\n今日係港島嘅人都知道<br />\n幾萬個人行咗港島線十鳩幾次係乜柒都無做過咁!!!<br />\n話就話快閃 但快閃咗d咩 達到咗咩目標? <br />\n<em>- 阻到交通? <br />\n可能少少但有好多路都通到而且夜晚無人<br />\n- 浪費警力撚狗? <br />\nD狗根本就係狗一直都無出過黎 淨係射幾粒煙就走撚晒<br />\n- 爭取到街坊支持? <br />\n除咗屌人影相同高空擲物外無任何行動 街方支持的前提喺要引狗入區 但d防暴連陣都無撚排過</em><br />\n<br />\n唯一成功嘅就係接近0拘捕0受傷<br />\n我知大家巳經失去咗好多手足 我亦唔鼓勵無目的送頭或留守 <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">其實今日某程度上嘅失敗係因為大家都唔知出黎做乜</span></span></strong><br />\n究竟係為撚狗? 定係打黑社會? 定係要破壞警署幫天水圍復仇? 定係齋坐示威? <br />\n由於無目標 每次行動同轉場都用咗好多時間 前線唔知快閃去到要做咩先叫成功所以後排係咁叫人走<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">所以我地之後既每次行動都應該要有一個目標 一個勝利既KPI 之後先再各自努力</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n呢個目標可以係好含糊但一定要有<br />\nE.g. 目標係快閃撚狗 - &gt; 就要撚到佢地出黎 然後走入民居 然後再轉場<br />\nE.g. 目標係阻塞交通 - &gt; 就唔好撚去狗屋"},{"pid":"f4d2e1f58f09915707a188dc27ea70a3ad1b9f55","tid":1418562,"uid":63747,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T19:13:50.000Z","msg":"<strong>2. 戰略上的失焦</strong><br />\n延伸(1.)<br />\n近幾日大家出黎行動都遇到咗戰略上的失焦<br />\n所謂既失焦唔係講要對準政府對準五大訴求果d<br />\n而係大家既行動變得非常非常被動<br />\n<em>例子:<br />\n- 85搞警署係因為琴晚有好多手足同女仔被不公平對待<br />\n- 84片地開花係因為西環將軍澳難攻<br />\n- 728去元朗係因為鄉黑打我地</em><br />\n<br />\n無錯 仇係要報<br />\n但我地總不能放棄一次又一次聚人嘅機會去做更多更大威力既行動<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">得罪講句 武力抗爭可能係呢一刻巳經到咗樽頸位<br />\n而家我地證明咗比對方睇我地有能力武裝<br />\n就唔需要再以單純既武力為目標<br />\n應以武力為手段去達成更大威脅力的行動</span></span></strong><br />\n<em>例如: (純9 up) <br />\n- 再闖立會宣佈成立臨時議會<br />\n- 入警署解救手足<br />\n- 圍堵鄭若驊要佢撤銷檢控<br />\n- 捉一隻狗出黎除衫示眾<br />\n- 唔比香港開市</em><br />\n<br />\n小弟自問無能力諗到咩有震脅力的行動 <br />\n但再被動式地復仇 再因為唔知邊個做咗d仆街事所以我地要討伐佢既話<br />\n我地好快就會墮入lucifer effect<br />\n被匿名同武力牽著走 失去中間淺黃支持<br />\n到時我地再諗到有咩核彈級行動都唔會動員到咁多人"},{"pid":"bc747c6f8a72c3f6de4a6e8de4c13db6238793c0","tid":1418562,"uid":63747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T19:14:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"54488a7a1f291ab2cbdc168cae0ba7050211aba1","tid":1418562,"uid":76543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T19:14:56.000Z","msg":"我哋不割蓆 不分化 不篤灰！！！！！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1415493\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1415493</a>"},{"pid":"6afdf73b1eb52c08fee2c2c32dd453331c6a8189","tid":1418562,"uid":63747,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T19:15:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d4cecc74692f204169a98161e96a4ee58de5dd83","tid":1418562,"uid":55918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T19:16:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b61a0b189d9f30160f72842a16129a139a75ebca","tid":1418562,"uid":55918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T19:16:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"899a0bc0888a191e6de29e89a16cc1189aebcb5d","tid":1418562,"uid":83164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T19:17:45.000Z","msg":"因為我地係香港人， 重要關頭先係考驗我地抗爭者的質素。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1418468\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1418468</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5af2fc394d7a60a9854f7a981ff8b2278ab8172e","tid":1418562,"uid":55918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T19:19:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4d93259e58237ed072c15efad46d27bad4f12b68","tid":1418562,"uid":238197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T19:21:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8c6a0c30ae45acda9d98e958784d2879b829c65b","tid":1418562,"uid":238197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T19:21:35.000Z","msg":"今日港島真心嬲"},{"pid":"80ad68d96028d88aef33ccf38d49620a2e0616e0","tid":1418562,"uid":22833,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T19:22:00.000Z","msg":"快閃北角真係有鬼！？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1418467\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1418467</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"40ae79f542e506681efd4e4ab20cc8cc07c77f7f","tid":1418562,"uid":238197,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T19:22:46.000Z","msg":"講完北角之後要認真討論之後去向"},{"pid":"49ba47adbea35fb4a584007fc5b172b034558d60","tid":1418562,"uid":157891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T19:25:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ba05ef8a0f7971adba151890f1249ddab36325c7","tid":1418562,"uid":138446,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T19:25:09.000Z","msg":"&lt;全部人同我入黎&gt; 下一步 廢除公安條例<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1418362\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1418362</a><br />\n<br />\n目標係度啊 T_T"},{"pid":"f8c4c89388bbd6b65b81c55d62f5c6fecc186a48","tid":1418562,"uid":63747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"40ae79f542e506681efd4e4ab20cc8cc07c77f7f","tid":1418562,"uid":238197,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T19:22:46.000Z","msg":"講完北角之後要認真討論之後去向"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T19:25:33.000Z","msg":"其實出黎前比人知道做咩好重要<br />\n例如 如果大家都知今日係想偷襲狗屋既話 就唔需要考慮去紅隧去銅鑼灣<br />\n咁巳經慳咗兩個鐘"},{"pid":"a47255e1e6a916513bb6f4eb23257ffb5f2445d8","tid":1418562,"uid":15897,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T19:26:11.000Z","msg":"要搞就一定有一個好明確既目標<br />\n今日係港島，一時又CWB，一時又北角，最後返咗去狗總<br />\n完全係漫冇目的咁鳩行"},{"pid":"a9affc7b361051d796965e2bcb2f5374e2f730b2","tid":1418562,"uid":63747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ba05ef8a0f7971adba151890f1249ddab36325c7","tid":1418562,"uid":138446,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T19:25:09.000Z","msg":"&lt;全部人同我入黎&gt; 下一步 廢除公安條例<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1418362\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1418362</a><br />\n<br />\n目標係度啊 T_T"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T19:26:49.000Z","msg":"認同!<br />\n不過就好似要再開新戰線咁"},{"pid":"01bc89fe25ac8637ed35b92f48e8a62c257a0a11","tid":1418562,"uid":76216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T19:27:13.000Z","msg":"建議］ p牌正負評顯示<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1415247\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1415247</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n目的唔係分化p牌會員<br />\n而係當你見到有大量p牌洗正負評時<br />\n要比平時更小心去做決定"},{"pid":"74179499d9b59e088fa6db44173f6506ad58bf37","tid":1418562,"uid":67553,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T19:27:13.000Z","msg":"「唔好畀仇恨支配」"},{"pid":"26a188184924b018bf38caee235109383f3410f4","tid":1418562,"uid":63747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a47255e1e6a916513bb6f4eb23257ffb5f2445d8","tid":1418562,"uid":15897,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T19:26:11.000Z","msg":"要搞就一定有一個好明確既目標<br />\n今日係港島，一時又CWB，一時又北角，最後返咗去狗總<br />\n完全係漫冇目的咁鳩行"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T19:28:09.000Z","msg":"快閃唔係問題<br />\n但要比前線做完想做既野先<br />\n<br />\n宏觀d睇要再探討做咩先更有力"},{"pid":"fa7e4f34a271f2e2fa0a30718652ea741fc345be","tid":1418562,"uid":246506,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T19:28:40.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n各位手足留意此人 係